Time flows upward.  Releases happen when all actions
below them are completed.

This document is at risk of radical change whenever I
feel like it.

-  means to do (unclaimed)

+  means done by Andy Balaam
A  means work in progress by Andy Balaam

x  means done by Sagar Shah
S  means work in progress by Sagar Shah

*  means done by Walter Duncan
W  means work in progress by Walter Duncan

^  means work done by Dave Torok
D  means work in progress by Dave Torok

